All Implemented Interfaces:
com.fasterxml.jackson.core.Versioned, Serializable
public class ReCodExApiMapper extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper
ReCodExApiMapper class is an extension of the Jackson ObjectMapper, intended to provide custom deserialization for the ReCodEx API. It's a singleton class, so it has one instance only.
